<h1 class="about-title">About Rent Spot</h1>

<p class="about-text">
Rent Spot is a simple PG and room booking platform where users can find
available PG accommodations, check details, view images, contact admin,
and book rooms easily.
</p>

<p class="about-text">
This website allows users to explore PG listings, view location on Google Maps,
check prices, and communicate with the admin for booking and payment confirmation.
</p>


<div class="about-features">

<h2>Website Features</h2>

<ul>

<li>User Registration and Login</li>
<li>Admin Approval System</li>
<li>PG Listing with Images</li>
<li>Google Map Location Button</li>
<li>UPI and QR Payment</li>
<li>User to Admin Messaging</li>
<li>Admin Notifications</li>
<li>Rating System</li>
<li>Mobile Responsive Design</li>

</ul>

